Kupocard Mini '19!

Until Wed., Jan. 30, 07:59 UTC

The Kupocard Mini is back as the limited-time Kupocard Mini '19 to welcome the new year!

In addition to granting you 800 Initial Gems and seven days of 100 Daily Gems, the Kupocard Mini '19 will also grant you 5 Chocobo Tail Feathers and 2 Relics of All Knowledge at the time of purchase! It will be here until Wed., Jan. 30, 07:59 UTC, so don't miss your chance!

About the Kupocard Mini '19

  • Kupocard Mini '19
    　　　　5 Chocobo Tail Feathers
    　　　　2 Relics of All Knowledge
    　　　　Initial Gems: 800
    　　　　Daily Gems: 100 (for 7 days)
    　　　　Total Gems: 1,500

Upon purchase, you will receive the Initial Gems immediately, and the Daily Gems will be sent to your Gift Box alongside your Daily Bonus from your next login, for a total of 7 logins.

After receiving the seventh Daily Gems reward, you can purchase another Kupocard Mini as long as it is within the campaign period. This means you can get up to five during this period!

* These logins do not need to be consecutive for you to receive all 7 login bonuses.
* Login bonuses reset at 08:00 UTC.
* You can confirm how many logins remain on your Kupocard(s) by tapping on the "Kupocards" button on the Gifts screen.
